{"tid":2043783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實啲美國人係咪收咗中國錢搞事搞暴動？","createTime":"2020-05-30T15:51:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T17:51:35.000Z","uid":187192,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bf6c44937b48f3f5aeaf5cc4f1cec6411a68fc38","tid":2043783,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:51:20.000Z","msg":"是咁的, 我係一個美國人<br />\n我見到有一班美國人喺度用黑人被警察殺害做籍口, 懷疑佢哋係收咗敵對國家嘅錢去搞事, 如果唔係，點解佢哋會有汽油彈？<br />\n有咁多木棒鐵棍去襲擊美國警察?<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪啲乜嘢(有關部門)提供咗幾千萬美金去贊助美國的暴徒去搞暴動？<br />\n<br />\n我成日睇鄧家彪youtube, 成日都話有好多外國勢力去分裂一個國家, 有好多秘密組織提供資金。我懷疑今次美國的暴動其實都係有其他國家去搞事, 可能會搞d 什麼顏色革命。<br />\n<br />\n有冇人知道今次美國暴動究竟係邊個國家提供資金?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3910290e98b2c9df3057bf816c5b3c847a8ab3ac","tid":2043783,"uid":16746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"一定是中国给钱"},{"pid":"f5ac92ba2dfeca99d6b56b36eefba3bb92e10a52","tid":2043783,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:13:13.000Z","msg":"究竟係邊個搞?"},{"pid":"fdd082f2fe4f2fbe1ec3471e43c41b7871f66fdf","tid":2043783,"uid":172190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:14:30.000Z","msg":"中國給美國錢<br />\n美國給中國錢<br />\n打和"},{"pid":"f3457133f875ddd0cc1df03ca89a3884b395a604","tid":2043783,"uid":106261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"美國太多敵人 估唔到邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71209a8171d5234d813c41d24d8f70d90e99b455","tid":2043783,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3457133f875ddd0cc1df03ca89a3884b395a604","tid":2043783,"uid":106261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T16:20:51.000Z","msg":"美國太多敵人 估唔到邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB